uttta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_extra_screenshot.png"><img class="size-large wp-image-10567 aligncenter" src="http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_extra_screenshot-1024x585.png" alt="" width="625" height="357" srcset="http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_extra_screenshot-1024x585.png 1024w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_extra_screenshot-300x171.png 300w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_extra_screenshot-624x356.png 624w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_extra_screenshot.png 1166w" sizes="(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px" /></a>The 3 features available now;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2015/10/19/no-emojis-were-speed-freakish/">remove Emoji&#8217;s</a></li>\n<li>remove (version parameter from the) query string (not that big a deal, from a load time perspective, but still)</li>\n<li>the ability to have Autoptimize add the <code>async</code> attribute to the local or 3rd party JavaScript (local JS-files will be excluded automatically if added here).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There&#8217;s one extra feature that will very likely be added; optimize Google Fonts (because removing them is considered harsh, apparently).</p>\n<p>Do download, do test and do let me know if anything is broken in the comments or via <a href="https://blog.futtta.be/contact/">my contact form</a>. And If you have other ideas for extra features, do let me know too!</p>\n<div class=''yarpp-related-rss''>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2012/11/06/dipping-below-the-magical-1-second-page-load-time/" rel="bookmark" title="Dipping below the magical 1 second page load time">Dipping below the magical 1 second page load time </a></li>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2013/04/01/easter-bunny-special-autoptimize-1-6-0/" rel="bookmark" title="Easter Bunny special: Autoptimize 1.6.0">Easter Bunny special: Autoptimize 1.6.0 </a></li>\n<li><a href="https://blog.futtta.be/2014/09/30/amazed-by-autoptimize/" rel="bookmark" title="Amazed by Autoptimize take-up">Amazed by Autoptimize take-up </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_autoptimize/~4/c8R3NQkEv2E" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:77:"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/11/29/another-autoptimize-experiment-extras/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"16";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/11/29/another-autoptimize-experiment-extras/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:66:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"Small experiment; Autoptimize with page cache";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/futtta_autoptimize/~3/UZAs4GkzvM0/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/11/16/small-experiment-autoptimize-with-page-cache/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"da