(2309, 1, '2018-01-30 12:46:56', '2018-01-30 12:46:56', '<h2>Apartment Emerald drop</h2>\r\nThe names of Bovec and the Soča Valley first associate with the Soča River. However Bovec land hides numerous other rivers and streams, waterfalls and lakes that you simply have to visit. We are sure that they will fascinate you with their purity and colour. This is our latest and most modern apartment. It was renovated and furnished in 2013. With modern approaches we have created a pleasant intimate atmosphere, which is best exemplified in a bedroom and bathroom harmony. The apartment is located on the ground floor and offers a pleasant stay also to the elderly.', 'Emerald drop', 'Apartment Emerald drop is our latest and most modern apartment. It was renovated and furnished in 2013. With modern approaches we have created a pleasant intimate atmosphere, which is best exemplified in a bedroom and bathroom harmony.', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'emerald-drop__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:16:31', '2018-02-12 09:16:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=cpo_portfolio&#038;p=2309', 0, 'cpo_portfolio', '', 0),
