(2318, 1, '2018-01-30 13:32:36', '2018-01-30 13:32:36', '<h2>Apartment Wild descent</h2>\r\nThe Soča Valley offers numerous possibilities for active holidays. You can go on a rafting or kayaking adventure on the Soča River, explore the hidden corners of unspoilt nature on a bike, if you would like a great dose of adrenalin you should try zip-lining. This is our most occupied apartment and is located on the top floor. It is suitable for families or groups of 4 and 6 people.', 'Wild Descent', 'Apartment Wild Descent is our most occupied apartment and is located on the top floor. It is suitable for families or groups of 4 and 6 people.', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wild-descent__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:16:31', '2018-02-12 09:16:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=cpo_portfolio&#038;p=2318', 0, 'cpo_portfolio', '', 0),
(2319, 1, '2018-01-30 13:40:01', '2018-01-30 13:40:01', '<h2>Apartma Aktivni počitek</h2>\r\nBovec nudi vsem športnim navdušencem številne možnosti preživljanja aktivnega dopusta, hkrati pa je Bovško s svojo neokrnjeno naravo in skritimi kotički idealna destinacija za vse, ki si želite miru in sprostitve v naravi. Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma.', 'Aktivni počitek', 'Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma.', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aktivni-pocitek__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:16:30', '2018-02-12 09:16:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=cpo_portfolio&#038;p=2319', 0, 'cpo_portfolio', '', 0),
(2320, 1, '2018-01-30 13:40:01', '2018-01-30 13:40:01', '<h2>Apartment Active rest</h2>\r\nBovec is a small paradise for all of you who wish to be active on your holidays, but at the same time Bovec land is, with its picturesque nature, hidden corners and stunning views, is a perfect destination for everybody who long for peace and quietness in unspoilt nature. Apartment Active rest was the first apartment we started renting in our house in 1980s. Located on the ground floor, it offers comfort of a home.', 'Active Rest', 'Apartment Active rest was the first apartment we started renting in our house in 1980s. Located on the ground floor, it offers comfort of a home.', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'active-rest__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:16:30', '2018-02-12 09:16:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=cpo_portfolio&#038;p=2320', 0, 'cpo_portfolio', '', 0),
