(2391, 1, '2018-01-31 13:32:34', '2018-01-31 13:32:34', '[ct_leading]Extra offers, which you''re provided with while staying at the Mrakič Apartments.[/ct_leading]\r\n\r\nExtra offers are available for all our guest during their staying in the Mrakič Apartments. We do out best that our guest receive first class care, so they can enjoy their relaxing or active vacations in the nature. Keeping guest needs in mind, we provide variety of offers, from culinary specialties to equipment rental, transfers across the destination of Bovec and tourist guidance.\r\n\r\n[ct_section title="Culinary" subtitle="Taste the Bovec specialties" background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\r\n\r\nCulinary as a experience is something many guest value the most on their vacations, and in the Mrakič Apartments, we provide just that - unique culinary experience for our guests in form of breakfasts, dinners and picnics, so guests can experience true flavour of traditional Bovec food.\r\n\r\n[ct_leading]Start your day full of energy with our delicious breakfasts.[/ct_leading]\r\n\r\n[ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-2491 size-medium" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/DSC_0040-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-2492 size-medium" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/DSC_0075-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-2493 size-medium" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/DSC_0054-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[ct_button url="/en/extra-offers/culinary/" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="" description="Click Here" size="normal" position="center" icon="" target="" rel="" class="section-cta"]Read More[/ct_button]\r\n\r\n[/ct_section]\r\n\r\n[ct_section title="Equipment rental" subtitle="Take full advantage of outdoor activities." background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\r\n\r\nEquipment rental is available for all our guest at the Mrakič apartments, the adults and their children, so they can enjoy in their daily sports activities and take full advantage of active vacations in the nature.\r\n\r\n[ct_leading]Experience unforgettable active vacations.[/ct_leading]\r\n\r\n[Modula id=''1'']\r\n\r\n[ct_spacer height="35"]\r\n\r\n[ct_button url="/en/extra-offers/equipment-rental/" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="" description="Click Here" size="normal" position="center" icon="" target="" rel="" class="section-cta"]Read More[/ct_button]\r\n\r\n[/ct_section]\r\n\r\n[ct_section title="Transfers" subtitle="Transfers across the destination of Bovec, free of charge." background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\r\n\r\nTransfers across the destination of Bovec are available for all the guests or Mrakič apartments, free of charge. Guests can therefore enjoy at their staying and take full advantage of exciting trips to the surrounding sightseeing and explore every hidden place of this beautiful valley of Bovec.\r\n\r\n[ct_leading]Whenever, wherever.[/ct_leading]\r\n\r\n[ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Free of charge" icon="money" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" class="is-flex" ]Transfers across the destination of Bovec are for out guests completely free of charge.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Fit for your needs" icon="random" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" class="is-flex" ]Transfers are arranged and scheduled so they fit all your plans and timings.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Comfortable" icon="check" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" class="is-flex" ]Instead of spending money for public transports, seat back, relax and enjoy in the comfortnes.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[ct_button url="/en/extra-offers/transfers/" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="" description="Click Here" size="normal" position="center" icon="" target="" rel="" class="section-cta"]Read More[/ct_button]\r\n\r\n[/ct_section]\r\n\r\n[ct_section title="Local tourism guidance" subtitle="Explore all the hidden spots of the destination Bovec" background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\r\n\r\nLocal tourism guidance is provided for all the guests of Mrakič Apartments. They can enjoy trips around the destination of Bovec in the present of expert tourist guide, so they can explore all the hidden gems of this beautiful Slovenian destination.\r\n\r\n[ct_leading]The hidden gems of the destination are available to you..[/ct_leading]\r\n\r\n[ct_button url="/en/extra-offers/local-tourism-guidance/" color="#efefef" background="#6a3e37" gradient="" description="Click Here" size="normal" position="center" icon="" target="" rel="" class="section-cta"]Read More[/ct_button]\r\n\r\n[/ct_section]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Extra offers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'extra-offers', '', '', '2018-02-02 13:15:49', '2018-02-02 13:15:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=2391', 0, 'page', '', 0),
