(2421, 1, '2018-02-01 11:59:19', '2018-02-01 11:59:19', '[ct_leading]Relaxation is the reason, why you took the vacation on the first place. In Mrakič apartments you will be able to relax in the friendly nature environment in the apartments garden, as well as take a refreshing and relaxing bath at our massage pools.[/ct_leading]\r\n\r\n[ct_separator title="" icon="arrow-down" style="normal" color="" top="" ][/ct_separator]\r\n\r\n[ct_section title="Massage pool" subtitle="Clear your mind and relax in our massage pool" background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\r\n\r\nEnvoy massage pool has incredible massage properties. With 43 massage nozzles and Moto-Massage DX massage system, you will feel like in a paradise. The comfort of pool bed and seating places offers you all the comfortness that you need in order to enjoy and relax. Gentle wrist massage and strong foot massage will relax and refresh your body. Envoy is not only beautiful, but elegant as well so is therefore ideal for hanging around the pool and relax.\r\n\r\n[ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="43 massage nozzles" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]Enjoy in therapeutical effects of massage nozzles and relax your body. [/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Choose massage type" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]Choose the type of massage you desire the most. Relieve your muscles with strong, sport massage or just enjoy and relax in the gentle, relaxing massage.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Comfort for perfect relaxation" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]The comfortness of massage pool will provide you with luxurious sensations.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[Modula id="3"]\r\n\r\n[/ct_section]\r\n\r\n[ct_section title="Garden and kids playground" subtitle="Enjoy in the nature, right in front of your apartment" background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\r\n\r\nA large garden is located right behind the apartments, which is moved away from the main road and hidden from public eye. You can relax in the shadow bellow the tree, read a book in the quite and peace or just enjoy your afternoon cup of coffee. A grill is available for you to use, so you can throw a picnic for your friends and family, while the kids are playing at the playground. A volleyball and badminton field is also available for use. The garden is meant for you, Dear guests, so use it and enjoy it.\r\n\r\n[ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Kids playground" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]The kids can play and enjoy at the playground, while you can take a time for yourself.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Volleyball and badminton field" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]Sport activites are an ideal way of spending free time in the nature.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[ct_feature title="Garden house" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]Use our grill and make yourself and your friends and family a wonderful dinner, which you can eat in the garden house, surrounded with wood and home-a-like atmosphere.[/ct_feature]\r\n\r\n[/ct_column_third_last]\r\n\r\n[Modula id="4"]\r\n\r\n[/ct_section]', 'Relaxation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'relaxation', '', '', '2018-02-05 11:52:01', '2018-02-05 11:52:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=2421', 0, 'page', '', 0),
