(2567, 1, '2018-02-05 11:50:21', '2018-02-05 11:50:21', '[ct_leading]Relaxation is the reason, why you took the vacation on the first place. In Mrakič apartments you will be able to relax in the friendly nature environment in the apartments garden, as well as take a refreshing and relaxing bath at our massage pools.[/ct_leading]\n\n[ct_separator title="" icon="arrow-down" style="normal" color="" top="" ][/ct_separator]\n\n[ct_section title="Massage pool" subtitle="Clear your mind and relax in out massage pool" background="" gradient="" color="light" padding="40px" ]\n\nEnvoy massage pool has incredible massage properties. With 43 massage nozzles and Moto-Massage DX massage system, you will feel like in a paradise. The comfort of pool bed and seating places offers you all the comfortness that you need in order to enjoy and relax. Gentle wrist massage and strong foot massage will relax and refresh your body. Envoy is not only beautiful, but elegant as well so is therefore ideal for hanging around the pool and relax.\n\n[ct_column_third]\n\n[ct_feature title="43 massage nozzles" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]Enjoy in therapeutical effects of massage nozzles and relax your body. [/ct_feature]\n\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third]\n\n[ct_feature title="Choose massage type" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]Choose the type of massage you desire the most. Relieve your muscles with strong, sport massage or just enjoy and relax in the gentle, relaxing massage.[/ct_feature]\n\n[/ct_column_third][ct_column_third_last]\n\n[ct_feature title="Comfort for perfect relaxation" icon="" color="#FFFFFF" background="#666666" gradient="#444444" image="" style="normal" ]The comfortness of massage pool will provide you with luxurious sensations.[/ct_feature]\n\n[/ct_column_third_last]\n\n[Modula id="3"]\n\n[/ct_section]\n\n[ct_section title="Garden and kids playground" subtitl