(2801, 1, '2018-02-09 12:58:56', '2018-02-09 12:58:56', '<h2>Apartma Gozdni sprehod</h2>\r\nBovec in Dolina Soče nudita nešteto skritih kotičkov, ki jih je vredno obiskati. Odpravite se na popoldanski sprehod po poteh, ki vas bodo pripeljale do številnih čudežev narave. Apartma Gozdni sprehod se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju hiše in nudi sproščujoč pogled na okoliške hribe. Je prostoren in udobno opremljen apartma, ki vas bo navdušil s številnimi detajli.', 'Apartma Gozdni sprehod', 'Apartma Gozdni sprehod se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju hiše in nudi sproščujoč pogled na okoliške hribe.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2766-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 12:58:56', '2018-02-09 12:58:56', '', 2766, 'http://localhost:8888/2766-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2802, 1, '2018-02-09 13:00:16', '2018-02-09 13:00:16', '<h2>Apartment Forrest stroll</h2>\r\nBovec and the Soča Valley offer countless hidden places that are worth visiting. Embark on an afternoon walk along the paths that will lead to many wonders of nature. Apartment Forest Stroll is located on the top floor of the house and offers a relaxing view of the surrounding mountains. It is a spacious and comfortably furnished apartment that will amaze you with many details.', 'Apartment Forest Stroll', 'Apartment Forest Stroll is located on the top floor and offers relaxing view on the surrounding hills and mountains. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2769-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 13:00:16', '2018-02-09 13:00:16', '', 2769, 'http://localhost:8888/2769-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2803, 1, '2018-02-09 13:01:09', '2018-02-09 13:01:09', '<h2>Apartma Aktivni počitek</h2>\r\nBovec nudi vsem športnim navdušencem številne možnosti preživljanja aktivnega dopusta, hkrati pa je Bovško s svojo neokrnjeno naravo in skritimi kotički idealna destinacija za vse, ki si želite miru in sprostitve v naravi. Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma.', 'Apartma Aktivni počitek', 'Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2778-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 13:01:09', '2018-02-09 13:01:09', '', 2778, 'http://localhost:8888/2778-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2804, 1, '2018-02-09 13:02:22', '2018-02-09 13:02:22', '<h2>Apartment Active rest</h2>\nBovec is a small paradise for all of you who wish to be active on your holidays, but at the same time Bovec land is, with its picturesque nature, hidden corners and stunning views, is a perfect destination for everybody who long for peace and quietness in unspoilt nature. Apartment Active rest was the first apartment we started renting in our house in 1980s. Located on the ground floor, it offers comfort of a home.', 'Apartment Active Rest', 'Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma. Apartment Active Rest was out first apartment available for rent. It is located on the ground floor and with bathroom attached to each room it offers the home-al', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2782-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 13:02:22', '2018-02-09 13:02:22', '', 2782, 'http://localhost:8888/2782-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
