(2809, 1, '2018-02-09 13:05:38', '2018-02-09 13:05:38', '<h2>Apartma Smaragdna kapljica</h2>\r\nOb imenu Bovec in Dolina Soče, seveda najprej pomislimo na reko Sočo. Vendar pa Bovško skriva se številne druge reke in potoke, slapove in jezera, ki jih morate obiskati, saj vas s svojo čistostjo in barvo gotovo ne bodo pustili ravnodušne. Naš najnovejši in najsodobnejši apartma prenovljen in opremljen leta 2013. S sodobnimi prijemi smo ustvarili prijetno intimno vzdušje, ki se najbolj odraža v sožitju spalnice in kopalnice. Apartma se nahaja v pritličju in nudi prijetno bivanje tudi za starejše.', 'Apartma Smaragdna kapljica', 'Apartma smaragdna kapljica je naš najnovejši in najsodobnejši apartma prenovljen in opremljen leta 2013. S sodobnimi prijemi smo ustvarili prijetno intimno vzdušje, ki se najbolj odraža v sožitju spalnice in kopalnice.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2789-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 13:05:38', '2018-02-09 13:05:38', '', 2789, 'http://localhost:8888/2789-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2810, 1, '2018-02-09 13:06:57', '2018-02-09 13:06:57', '<h2>Apartment Emerald drop</h2>\nThe names of Bovec and the Soča Valley first associate with the Soča River. However Bovec land hides numerous other rivers and streams, waterfalls and lakes that you simply have to visit. We are sure that they will fascinate you with their purity and colour. This is our latest and most modern apartment. It was renovated and furnished in 2013. With modern approaches we have created a pleasant intimate atmosphere, which is best exemplified in a bedroom and bathroom harmony. The apartment is located on the ground floor and offers a pleasant stay also to the elderly', 'Apartment Emerald Drop', 'Apartma smaragdna kapljica je naš najnovejši in najsodobnejši apartma prenovljen in opremljen leta 2013. S sodobnimi prijemi smo ustvarili prijetno intimno vzdušje, ki se najbolj odraža v sožitju spalnice in kopalnice. Apartment Emerald Drop is our newest and most modern apartment, completly renovated and re-equiped in 2013. With modern aproaches we were able to create private, initim', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2791-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 13:06:57', '2018-02-09 13:06:57', '', 2791, 'http://localhost:8888/2791-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
