(2835, 1, '2018-02-12 09:49:34', '2018-02-12 09:49:34', '<h2>Apartma Gozdni sprehod</h2>\r\nBovec in Dolina Soče nudita nešteto skritih kotičkov, ki jih je vredno obiskati. Odpravite se na popoldanski sprehod po poteh, ki vas bodo pripeljale do številnih čudežev narave. Apartma Gozdni sprehod se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju hiše in nudi sproščujoč pogled na okoliške hribe. Je prostoren in udobno opremljen apartma, ki vas bo navdušil s številnimi detajli.', 'Apartma Gozdni sprehod', 'Apartma Gozdni sprehod se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju hiše in nudi sproščujoč pogled na okoliške hribe.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2766-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:49:34', '2018-02-12 09:49:34', '', 2766, 'http://localhost:8888/2766-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2836, 1, '2018-02-12 09:49:57', '2018-02-12 09:49:57', '<h2>Apartma Gozdni sprehod</h2>\r\nBovec in Dolina Soče nudita nešteto skritih kotičkov, ki jih je vredno obiskati. Odpravite se na popoldanski sprehod po poteh, ki vas bodo pripeljale do številnih čudežev narave. Apartma Gozdni sprehod se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju hiše in nudi sproščujoč pogled na okoliške hribe. Je prostoren in udobno opremljen apartma, ki vas bo navdušil s številnimi detajli.', 'Apartma Gozdni sprehod', 'Apartma Gozdni sprehod se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju hiše in nudi sproščujoč pogled na okoliške hribe.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2766-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:49:57', '2018-02-12 09:49:57', '', 2766, 'http://localhost:8888/2766-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2837, 1, '2018-02-12 09:52:05', '2018-02-12 09:52:05', '<h2>Apartment Forrest stroll</h2>\r\nBovec and the Soča Valley offer countless hidden places that are worth visiting. Embark on an afternoon walk along the paths that will lead to many wonders of nature. Apartment Forest Stroll is located on the top floor of the house and offers a relaxing view of the surrounding mountains. It is a spacious and comfortably furnished apartment that will amaze you with many details.', 'Apartment Forest Stroll', 'Apartment Forest Stroll is located on the top floor and offers relaxing view on the surrounding hills and mountains. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2769-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:52:05', '2018-02-12 09:52:05', '', 2769, 'http://localhost:8888/2769-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2838, 1, '2018-02-12 09:53:46', '2018-02-12 09:53:46', '<h2>Apartma Aktivni počitek</h2>\r\nBovec nudi vsem športnim navdušencem številne možnosti preživljanja aktivnega dopusta, hkrati pa je Bovško s svojo neokrnjeno naravo in skritimi kotički idealna destinacija za vse, ki si želite miru in sprostitve v naravi. Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma.', 'Apartma Aktivni počitek', 'Apartma Aktivni počitek je bil prvi apartma, ki smo ga zaceli oddajati v naši hiši. Nahaja se v pritličju in s tremi kopalnicami nudi udobje kot doma.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2778-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:53:46', '2018-02-12 09:53:46', '', 2778, 'http://localhost:8888/2778-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2839, 1, '2018-02-12 09:54:34', '2018-02-12 09:54:34', '<h2>Apartment Active rest</h2>\r\nBovec is a small paradise for all of you who wish to be active on your holidays, but at the same time Bovec land is, with its picturesque nature, hidden corners and stunning views, is a perfect destination for everybody who long for peace and quietness in unspoilt nature. Apartment Active rest was the first apartment we started renting in our house in 1980s. Located on the ground floor, it offers comfort of a home.', 'Apartment Active Rest', 'Apartment Active Rest was out first apartment available for rent. It is located on the ground floor and with bathroom attached to each room it offers the home alike luxury.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2782-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:54:34', '2018-02-12 09:54:34', '', 2782, 'http://localhost:8888/2782-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2840, 1, '2018-02-12 09:56:11', '2018-02-12 09:56:11', '<h2>Apartma Divji spust</h2>\r\nDolina Soče nudi številne možnosti za aktiven dopust. Lahko se s čolni spustite po reki Soči, s kolesom spoznavate neokrnjeno naravo, tisti bolj avanturistični pa se spustite po jeklenicah nad Bovcem. Naš najbolj zaseden apartma se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju in je primeren za družine ali skupine med 4 in 6 oseb.', 'Apartma Divji spust', 'Apartma Divji spust je naš najbolj zaseden apartma se nahaja v zgornjem nadstropju in je primeren za družine ali skupine med 4 in 6 oseb.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2784-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:56:11', '2018-02-12 09:56:11', '', 2784, 'http://localhost:8888/2784-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2841, 1, '2018-02-12 09:57:35', '2018-02-12 09:57:35', '<h2>Apartment Wild descent</h2>\r\nThe Soča Valley offers numerous possibilities for active holidays. You can go on a rafting or kayaking adventure on the Soča River, explore the hidden corners of unspoilt nature on a bike, if you would like a great dose of adrenalin you should try zip-lining. This is our most occupied apartment and is located on the top floor. It is suitable for families or groups of 4 and 6 people.', 'Apartment Wild Descent', 'Apartment Wild Descent is our most booked apartment and it is located on the top floor. Apartment is ideal for families and groups between 4 to 6 people.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2786-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:57:35', '2018-02-12 09:57:35', '', 2786, 'http://localhost:8888/2786-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2842, 1, '2018-02-12 09:59:00', '2018-02-12 09:59:00', '<h2>Apartma Smaragdna kapljica</h2>\r\nOb imenu Bovec in Dolina Soče, seveda najprej pomislimo na reko Sočo. Vendar pa Bovško skriva se številne druge reke in potoke, slapove in jezera, ki jih morate obiskati, saj vas s svojo čistostjo in barvo gotovo ne bodo pustili ravnodušne. Naš najnovejši in najsodobnejši apartma prenovljen in opremljen leta 2013. S sodobnimi prijemi smo ustvarili prijetno intimno vzdušje, ki se najbolj odraža v sožitju spalnice in kopalnice. Apartma se nahaja v pritličju in nudi prijetno bivanje tudi za starejše.', 'Apartma Smaragdna kapljica', 'Apartma smaragdna kapljica je naš najnovejši in najsodobnejši apartma prenovljen in opremljen leta 2013. S sodobnimi prijemi smo ustvarili prijetno intimno vzdušje, ki se najbolj odraža v sožitju spalnice in kopalnice.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2789-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:59:00', '2018-02-12 09:59:00', '', 2789, 'http://localhost:8888/2789-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2843, 1, '2018-02-12 09:59:35', '2018-02-12 09:59:35', '<h2>Apartment Emerald drop</h2>\r\nThe names of Bovec and the Soča Valley first associate with the Soča River. However Bovec land hides numerous other rivers and streams, waterfalls and lakes that you simply have to visit. We are sure that they will fascinate you with their purity and colour. This is our latest and most modern apartment. It was renovated and furnished in 2013. With modern approaches we have created a pleasant intimate atmosphere, which is best exemplified in a bedroom and bathroom harmony. The apartment is located on the ground floor and offers a pleasant stay also to the elderly', 'Apartment Emerald Drop', 'Apartment Emerald Drop is our newest and most modern apartment, completly renovated and re-equiped in 2013. With modern aproaches we were able to create private, initimate atmosphere, which is most noticeable in coexistence of bedroom and bathroom.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2791-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-12 09:59:35', '2018-02-12 09:59:35', '', 2791, 'http://localhost:8888/2791-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
